					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system initiates a session lock after a 15-minute period of inactivity for all connection types. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the operating system to initiate a session lock after a 15-minute period of inactivity for all connection types.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
