					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the operating system to provide the capability to centrally review and analyze audit records from multiple components within the system.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
