					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system uses multifactor authentication for network access to privileged accounts. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the operating system to use multifactor authentication for network access to privileged accounts.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
