					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system uses multifactor authentication for local access to nonprivileged accounts. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
