  XO auth-ldap Plugin: ACTIVE
  Source: LDAP-authenticated users detected via REST API
  [PASS] Account management delegated to AD; AD provides account creation audit trails and notification via Windows Security Event Log

COMPENSATING CONTROL: User account management is delegated to Active Directory
via the XO auth-ldap plugin. AD logs all account creation events in the Windows
Security Event Log (Event IDs 4720/4722) and can trigger notifications to SAs/ISSOs
via Group Policy, SIEM integration, or email alerting rules.
