					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system notifies System Administrators and Information System Security Officers for account removal actions. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
