					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system prevents the installation of patches, service packs, device drivers, or operating system components without verification they have been digitally signed using a certificate that is recognized and approved by the organization. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
