					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system implements cryptographic mechanisms to protect the confidentiality of nonlocal maintenance and diagnostic communications, when used for nonlocal maintenance sessions. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
