					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system implements cryptographic mechanisms to prevent unauthorized disclosure of information and/or detect changes to information during transmission unless otherwise protected by alternative physical safeguards, such as, at a  minimum, a Protected Distribution System (PDS). 

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
