				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the operating system to use a patch management system to ensure security-relevant updates are installed within the time period directed by the authoritative source.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
